From 1e8e2e941c9593a900bffe5ee67f256263ce9960 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alp Lab AB <gate@alp-lab.se>
Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 22:08:12 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] drm: renesas: rzg2l-mipi-dsi: pm_runtime-guard host transfer
 to avoid SError at shutdown

A DCS transfer can be issued while the DSI host is runtime suspended --
e.g. drm_panel_disable() from a panel .shutdown() during
device_shutdown(), after the display pipeline has already powered the
link down. rzg2l_mipi_pm_runtime_suspend() holds the host in reset
(reset_control_assert), so the register writes in
rzg2l_mipi_dsi_host_transfer() fault with an asynchronous SError that
panics the kernel mid-reboot (RZ/V2N E1M board: hx8394 panel
.shutdown), and the reboot never completes.

Resume the host across the register accesses so a transfer is safe in
any PM state; the bounded SQCH0SR completion poll then simply times out
harmlessly when the link is down.

Upstream-Status: Pending

Signed-off-by: Alp Lab AB
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/renesas/rz-du/rzg2l_mipi_dsi.c | 15 +++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 15 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/renesas/rz-du/rzg2l_mipi_dsi.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/renesas/rz-du/rzg2l_mipi_dsi.c
index 3062088d8913..b00376119eed 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/renesas/rz-du/rzg2l_mipi_dsi.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/renesas/rz-du/rzg2l_mipi_dsi.c
@@ -1196,6 +1196,19 @@ static ssize_t rzg2l_mipi_dsi_host_transfer(struct mipi_dsi_host *host,
 		value |= SQCH0DSC0AR_FMT_SHORT;
 	}
 
+	/*
+	 * A DCS transfer may be issued while the DSI host is runtime
+	 * suspended -- e.g. drm_panel_disable() from a panel's .shutdown()
+	 * during device_shutdown(), after the display pipeline has already
+	 * powered the link down. The host registers are held in reset while
+	 * suspended, so touching them faults with an asynchronous SError.
+	 * Resume the host across the register accesses so a transfer is safe
+	 * in any PM state.
+	 */
+	ret = pm_runtime_resume_and_get(dsi->dev);
+	if (ret < 0)
+		return ret;
+
 	rzg2l_mipi_dsi_link_write(dsi, SQCH0DSC0AR, value);
 
 	/*
@@ -1236,6 +1249,8 @@ static ssize_t rzg2l_mipi_dsi_host_transfer(struct mipi_dsi_host *host,
 			ret = packet.payload_length;
 	}
 
+	pm_runtime_put(dsi->dev);
+
 	return ret;
 }
 
